1993
02:12:16,080 --> 02:12:17,040
<i>"Families are torn apart. "</i>

1994
02:12:17,160 --> 02:12:19,800
<i>"If only I can be myself, I'll be satisfied.</i>

1995
02:12:19,920 --> 02:12:21,560
<i>"I know that I'm a woman
